<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4f46e5;
            --background: #f8fafc;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #0f172a;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background);
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 900px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 3rem;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #06b6d4 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f1f5f9;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .tech-badge-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .tech-badge {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: var(--text-main);
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>About This Assignment</h1>
        <p>This web application is developed to meet the specifications of <b>Assignment 10 (Node & Express)</b>. It demonstrates robust implementations of Model-View-Controller (MVC) architecture, custom logging and entry validation middlewares, EJS template parsing, and RESTful routing hierarchies.</p>
        
        <p>By splitting business logic into individual routes and controllers, the project maintains separation of concerns, ensuring high code readability, fast load performance, and modular extensibility.</p>
        
        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.2rem;">Technologies Used:</h3>
        <div class="tech-badge-container">
            <span class="tech-badge">Node.js</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Express Framework</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Embedded JavaScript (EJS)</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">Custom Middlewares</span>
            <span class="tech-badge">In-Memory Arrays</span>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
